&lt;/a>&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>蓝牙发展历程--1999到2025</title><link>https://tingxuanr.github.io/note/%E8%93%9D%E7%89%99%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E5%8E%86%E7%A8%8B--1999%E5%88%B02025/</link><pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 14:43:42 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://tingxuanr.github.io/note/%E8%93%9D%E7%89%99%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E5%8E%86%E7%A8%8B--1999%E5%88%B02025/</guid><description>&lt;p>摘要：随着蓝牙6.0对UWB级测距能力的整合，以及LE Audio重塑无线音视频体验，蓝牙正突破“连接工具”的定位，向环境感知与空间计算领域纵深拓展，成为构建智能世界的隐形桥梁。本文简要介绍蓝牙从1.0到6.0的发展历史。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Mac时间错误</title><link>https://tingxuanr.github.io/note/mac%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%E9%94%99%E8%AF%AF/</link><pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 20:45:24 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://tingxuanr.github.io/note/mac%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%E9%94%99%E8%AF%AF/</guid><description>&lt;p>摘要：Mac时间突然错误，需要删除timed才能校正。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>区块链与比特币</title><link>https://tingxuanr.github.io/note/%E5%8C%BA%E5%9D%97%E9%93%BE%E4%B8%8E%E6%AF%94%E7%89%B9%E5%B8%81/</link><pubDate>Sun, 26 Jan 2025 10:16:20 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://tingxuanr.github.io/note/%E5%8C%BA%E5%9D%97%E9%93%BE%E4%B8%8E%E6%AF%94%E7%89%B9%E5%B8%81/</guid><description>&lt;p>摘要：摘录了阮一峰写的关于区块链和比特币的一些知识。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>图片在显示器上在为什么会糊？PPI、DPI、Retina</title><link>https://tingxuanr.github.io/note/%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87%E5%9C%A8%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E5%99%A8%E4%B8%8A%E5%9C%A8%E4%B8%BA%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E4%BC%9A%E7%B3%8Appidpiretina/</link><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 12:41:19 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://tingxuanr.github.io/note/%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87%E5%9C%A8%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E5%99%A8%E4%B8%8A%E5%9C%A8%E4%B8%BA%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E4%BC%9A%E7%B3%8Appidpiretina/</guid><description>&lt;p>摘要：有关图片的缩放及Retina屏幕介绍&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>混乱的分辨率：1920*1080=2K ？</title><link>https://tingxuanr.github.io/note/%E6%B7%B7%E4%B9%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%88%86%E8%BE%A8%E7%8E%87192010802k-/</link><pubDate>Sun, 12 Jan 2025 18:06:07 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://tingxuanr.github.io/note/%E6%B7%B7%E4%B9%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%88%86%E8%BE%A8%E7%8E%87192010802k-/</guid><description>&lt;p>摘要：大多数人的认知里，1920x1080应该是1080p，而非2K。但是数字电影联盟的标准里2K却是2048x1080。这其实是电影行业和显示器行业标准不同导致。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>视频为什么会糊？蓝光、码率、分辨率</title><link>https://tingxuanr.github.io/note/%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91%E4%B8%BA%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E4%BC%9A%E7%B3%8A%E8%93%9D%E5%85%89%E7%A0%81%E7%8E%87%E5%88%86%E8%BE%A8%E7%8E%87/</link><pubDate>Sat, 11 Jan 2025 17:57:20 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://tingxuanr.github.io/note/%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91%E4%B8%BA%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E4%BC%9A%E7%B3%8A%E8%93%9D%E5%85%89%E7%A0%81%E7%8E%87%E5%88%86%E8%BE%A8%E7%8E%87/</guid><description>&lt;p>摘要：主要介绍一下什么是蓝光、码率、分辨率，以及它们之间的区别。重点介绍码率和蓝光，分辨率太混乱，单独介绍。&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>